---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Fernwood Coffee — About">
  <section class="about">
    <h1>Our Story</h1>
    <p>
      Fernwood Coffee opened in 2016 in a small corner unit that used to be a
      bicycle repair shop. The espresso machine came before the chairs did — we
      served coffee out of the doorway for the first two months while the
      renovation finished around us.
    </p>
    <p>
      We roast in small batches, change the pastry case daily, and still grind
      every order by hand. Nothing here is automated, including the music — it's
      just whatever the person behind the counter feels like playing that day.
    </p>
    <p>
      This page (and the whole site) is a practice project built with Astro. The
      shop, the menu, and the story are all fictional.
    </p>
  </section>

  <style>
    .about {
      max-width: 640px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 3rem 0 4rem;
    }

    .about p {
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
